Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The conflict began from a single spark,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and has grown into a massive war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A multitude of people had myriad\N hopes and dreams that were at odds,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}resulting in great tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a sad thing indeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This war has brought me great sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel both shame and a deep regret\Nover our use of power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that was not meant for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...succeed the previous emperor,\NRayregalia Vers Rayvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and name myself Empress\Nof the Vers Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also take Count Cruhteo, member of the\NOrbital Knights' 37 Clans, to be my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We, the imperial family of the Vers Empire,\Nwish to make peace with Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Empress of Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I command all Orbital Knights who\Nare listening to this transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to cease hostilities immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Princess Asseylum going to found\Na new dynasty with Lord Troyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the all-out\Noffensive on the UFE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Do nothing for now.\NWe'll see which way the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known.\NLord Troyard was a lowborn Terran.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His attempts to inveigle his way into\Nthe imperial family are offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!\NSir Harklight, we're returning to base!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.00,T1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting Star of Yesteryear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are they still fighting?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The princess just declared\Nthat they must stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moonbase's forces\Nare still itching for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay sharp, everyone!\NThe battle isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Princess Asseylum just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that Empress Asseylum\Nwas the princess I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just as Lt. Kaizuka predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then that cease-fire\Norder was also genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies in front of us don't seem \Ninterested in laying down arms, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any word from HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No instructions, ma'am.\NSo it's "continue operation."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the moonbase nor Landing Castles\Nare showing any intent to cease hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Empress Asseylum's location?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That transmission originated from\NCount Mazuurek's Landing Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's abandoned the Moon?\NOr has there been a split?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Troyard, what of\NEmpress Asseylum's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Order? What order?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.\NI didn't think her capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is truly important\Nis the imperial family's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you still have\NAldnoah activation privileges,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can you not still\Nmake your dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is the only place\Nthat I can call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness is touching,\NPrincess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a terrible thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen a great many things\Nwhile flying among those lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The future...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of it, both good and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only the immediate future can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many things unfolded\Nexactly as I foresaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I failed to see what was truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rearm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Troyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Princess Asseylum\Nsay such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patch this through the command center.\NI will address all our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The deployed Stygis Squadron, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me! Get clear of the moonbase\Nin the next 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender to the UFE\Nalong with the Landing Castles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will abandon the moonbase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Lemrina...\NI apologize for the many wrongs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have done you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May you remain in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harklight, please escort\NPrincess Lemrina to a shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Highness, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine! Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple new signatures detected\Nleaving the moonbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're leaving the combat zone, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moonbase...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did we beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're making it self-destruct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Harklight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See to the shuttle's defense!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Harklight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing? Turn back.\NI thought I ordered you to surrender.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harklight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stygis Squadron!\NDon't act without orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy reinforcements closing in.\N10 o'clock. Angle of elevation, -10!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by to engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! We no longer have\Nany hope of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw your lives away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made my peace with death\Nlong ago, Lord.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me this one selfish act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surrender, Harklight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg your pardon, Milord Slaine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot comply with that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here they come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All units, scatter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could they do this?\NDamn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is still something that I must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've come for you,\NSlaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this once and for all,\NInaho Kaizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you predict my attacks,\Nthere's no point if you can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opening contact channel.\NDecrypting protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think it will do any good,\Nbut I'll ask anyway. Surrender, Slaine Troyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way to say\Nsuch a pointless thing to me, Inaho Kaizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have a different objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappoint me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... My monitors are damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know... You can't do\Nany more high-load processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut all predictive imagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...have any need for a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 o'clock! Angle of elevation, 5! Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ahead, emergency speed!\NCome about, 060!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coming about, 060!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Load canister shot!\NFire once targets are locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao's combat data is stored\Nin the tactical data link.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All units, refer to that and–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barouhcruz, member of the\NOrbital Knights 37 Clans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I cut in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Barouhcruz...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8 o'clock! Angle of elevation, -25! Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining rounds, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be gained\Nby continuing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed. But there's nothing\Nto be lost by it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to despair\Nis a foolish choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it!\NThis is the choice I wanted the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slice them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rayet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Radar returns\Napproaching at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Tharsis...\Nand a UFE Kataphrakt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rayet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three-direction crossfire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MRSI, neutralize target, auto fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always hated that color!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The drones are on autopilot!\NUse the boulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can limit the direction of their attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. I only lost an arm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Harklight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle status?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Including myself,\N3 Stygis Masters remain,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as well as some 6 Slaves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rest have been downed by the UFE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have fired most of my bullets as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Barouhcruz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Octantis' right\Narm is nonfunctional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must have been damaged\Nin that last attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These Terran warriors\Nare not without skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is Lord Slaine's\Nbirthplace, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Do not try to fight\Nan Olympian sandstorm," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We seem to have\Nmisread the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's have another go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall join you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9 o'clock! Angle of elevation, 20!\NEnemy formation closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All guns, take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kataphrakt platoons!\NAll units, fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll act as a drogue chute.\NIt will stabilize you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to die with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll burn up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kataphrakt frames are high density.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll work well enough\Nas ablative shielding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... It can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah Reactor #1, constructed as a sign\Nof goodwill between Earth and Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is scheduled to be activated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're told that Empress Asseylum herself\Nwill participate in the activation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Research into making activation privileges\Nuniversal so that anyone can do it is still ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens,\Nindustries using Aldnoah will develop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and will help greatly\Nwith Earth's reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And as the nation that produces Aldnoah,\Nit should also prove to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,an effective means for the Vers\NEmpire to earn foreign capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Troyard's theories have\Nalready been proven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so we should see them put into\Npractice in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's ironic that Slaine Troyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the son of that same Dr. Troyard,\Nplotted the assassination of Empress Asseylum,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which was the trigger for\NInterplanetary War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard's death allowed Earth\Nand Vers to conclude a friendship treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but there are still Mars Knights\Nwho occupy territory on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One goal of Empress Asseylum's visit\Nis peace negotiations with those knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:18:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's hoping that we'll be seeing\Nthe prompt return of that occupied territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the hope that this light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will be a bridge of peace\Nbetween Earth and Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,....awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really should eat your meals, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The warden has been complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from when I shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An analytical engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bio-device implanted\Nthat was neuro-linked to my cranial nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I had it removed.\NI don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't it been long enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I deceived, I stole, I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrificed many of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. You're going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have one more favor to ask of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's what Princess Asseylum wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Save Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Save him from the chains of misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seylum asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The blue sky and sea go on forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that the blue sky is the result\Nof something called Rayleigh scattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I visited Earth last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a Terran I had befriended\Nwas kind enough to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lovely memory.
